Welcome to Grey Shield Research LLC.

This company was started with one goal in mind, to make correctional data understandable, and more importantly, useful. Whether you are the manager of prison, jail, lockup, pre-trial services agency, or even police department, we offer premium and budget data analysis services!

Discounts offered for unique projects!

